transcripts.text: Hi, how's it going, sir?  Can I please have your name and your position here?
No, you can't record inside a federal building.  If you're not going to turn recording off, we'll just have to call the Federal Protective Service.  Well...

Hey, what's going on, guys?  It's Auditing America.  We're in the state of Massachusetts.  I'm out with Josh from Accountability for All and with Hot Toe Truck Girl.  We're doing a First Amendment audit.  We're going to see if they respect our First Amendment rights.  What's upstairs?  Is that the immigration?
